 e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s6.e8" /></sentence><sentence text=" The 16 cases of statin-clarithromycin adverse drug reactions (rhabdomyolysis (n = 14) or less severe clinical myopathy) involved a CYP3A4-metabolized statin (simvastatin, lovastatin or atorvastatin)"><entity charOffset="24-38" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" text="clarithromycin" /><entity charOffset="159-170" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" text="simvastatin" /><entity charOffset="172-182" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" text="lovastatin" /><entity charOffset="186-198" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e3" text="atorvastatin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" /><pair ddi="true" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" /><pair ddi="true" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" /><pair ddi="true" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e3" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e3" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e2" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s7.e3" /></sentence><sentence text=" In line, a cohort study found concurrent use of clarithromycin and CYP3A4-metabolized statins to be associated with a doubled risk of hospitalization with rhabdomyolysis or other statin-related adverse events as compared with azithromycin-statin co-administration"><entity charOffset="49-63" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e0" text="clarithromycin" /><entity charOffset="227-239" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e1" text="azithromycin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e0" /><pair ddi="true" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s8.e1" /></sentence><sentence text=" If clarithromycin is necessary, we recommend (a) avoiding co-administration with simvastatin, lovastatin or atorvastatin; (b) withholding or dose-reducing pitavastatin; (c) continuing pravastatin therapy with caution, limiting pravastatin dose to 40 mg daily; and (d) continuing fluvastatin or rosuvastatin with caution"><entity charOffset="4-18" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" text="clarithromycin" /><entity charOffset="82-93" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" text="simvastatin" /><entity charOffset="95-105" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e2" text="lovastatin" /><entity charOffset="109-121" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e3" text="atorvastatin" /><entity charOffset="156-168" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e4" text="pitavastatin" /><entity charOffset="185-196" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e5" text="pravastatin" /><entity charOffset="228-239" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e6" text="pravastatin" /><entity charOffset="280-291" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e7" text="fluvastatin" /><entity charOffset="295-307" id="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e8" text="rosuvastatin" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e3" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e4" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e5" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e6" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e7" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e0" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e8" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e2" /><pair ddi="false" e1="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e1" e2="DDI-PubMed.31628882.s9.e3"